default6.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn any event the Court was in 
defaultno 
defaultdoubt as to the appropriateness of the charity bringing these important issues to its attention.  Mr Justice Munby stated:
default&#xa0;
default “
defaultThe proceedings have been brought by The Howard League for Penal Reform whose history and credentials need no introduction. It undoubtedly is, as it claims to be, the leading non-governmental organisation in this country concerned with penal issues and pol
defaulticy. Here I need only to note that in the last decade or so it has had a particular focus on children and young people in the criminal justice system. 
default“
defaultIt is not disputed by the defendant that the Howard League has a “sufficient interest” in the matter so
default as to give it locus to make the current application: 
defaultR v Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs ex p World Development Movement Ltd 
default[1995] 1 WLR 386 and 
defaultR v Somerset County Council ex p Dixon 
default[1998] Env LR 111.
default”
